txt_content:
 本帖最后由 gooding300 于 2016-2-9 19:39 编辑 

刚才翻看论坛时无意间在"皮肤发布"模板中看到了一句话
双层皮肤仅适用于Minecraft 1.7.6及之后版本复制代码
而事实应该是“双层皮肤仅适用于Minecraft 1.8及之后版本”


以下有两点证据，如果需要的话还可以通过实测来加入第三点证据：
1.反编译Minecraft
1) 1.7.10 bmc.class (MCP反混淆后为net/minecraft/client/renderer/ImageBufferDownload.java)
这是一个将获取到的皮肤图像转换为Minecraft可识别的标准皮肤图像的类
Line25: this.imageWidth = 64;
Line26: this.imageHeight = 32;复制代码众所周知，双层皮肤是长宽相等的(默认64*64)，64*32毫无疑问还是单层皮肤。


2) 1.8 ckr.class (MCP反混淆后为net/minecraft/client/renderer/ImageBufferDownload.java)
与上面的为同一个文件
Line25: this.imageWidth = 64;
Line26: his.imageHeight = 64;复制代码此时才转变成双层格式。
且此文件中还有将32*64的单层皮肤转换为双层的代码
Line30-44
                if (bufferedimage.getHeight() == 32)
                {
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 24, 48, 20, 52, 4, 16, 8, 20, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 28, 48, 24, 52, 8, 16, 12, 20, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 20, 52, 16, 64, 8, 20, 12, 32, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 24, 52, 20, 64, 4, 20, 8, 32, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 28, 52, 24, 64, 0, 20, 4, 32, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 32, 52, 28, 64, 12, 20, 16, 32, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 40, 48, 36, 52, 44, 16, 48, 20, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 44, 48, 40, 52, 48, 16, 52, 20, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 36, 52, 32, 64, 48, 20, 52, 32, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 40, 52, 36, 64, 44, 20, 48, 32, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 44, 52, 40, 64, 40, 20, 44, 32, null);
                        g.drawImage(bufferedimage1, 48, 52, 44, 64, 52, 20, 56, 32, null);
                }复制代码

相信以上1.7.10与1.8的部分反编译代码可以证明双层皮肤是在1.8才开始支持的，而不是所谓的1.7.6
注：行数由于反编译程序的不同可能会有出入


2.Minecraft Wiki
中文：http://minecraft-zh.gamepedia.com/%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4
历史
1.8
14w03a
皮肤获得了一次改革；右边和左边的脚/手臂现在可以被独立编辑了，帽子层现在覆盖了整个身体，这意味着现在可以覆盖皮肤了。这也就意味着独立的 Minecraft 皮肤数量由原来的 2.29×1011,328 提高到 3.06×1023,581。复制代码英文：http://minecraft.gamepedia.com/Skin
History
1.8
14w03a
Skins have received an overhaul; right and left legs/arms can now be edited independently and the hat layer now counts for the whole body, meaning overlays can now be added on skins. This means there are now up to 3.06×1023,581 unique Minecraft skins instead of 2.29×1011,328 previously.复制代码
